{"tid":2298543,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"資深投資者蔡志忠妻確診 胡應湘妻否認是「麻雀腳」","createTime":"2020-11-24T06:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T06:29:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d751297bf49fb913c5661e09a5c2efdebd8a748f","tid":2298543,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:29:14.000Z","msg":"本港疫情再創新高，當中更有多位城中名媛確診。資深投資者、亞洲地產創辦人蔡志忠向生意夥伴發訊息指，太太確診新冠肺炎，而自己則仍在檢測中，惟訊息未有透露是否與歌舞群組有關。蔡志忠接受《蘋果》查詢時證實妻子及工人已確診，而自己身體並無異樣，目前正進行自我隔離。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201124/R5SJE5VQZZANNDLRTQTOWQGUD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201124%2FR5SJE5VQZZANNDLRTQTOWQGUD4%2F&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=0587379f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201124%2FR5SJE5VQZZANNDLRTQTOWQGUD4%2F&h=9f29d3c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201124/R5SJE5VQZZANNDLRTQTOWQGUD4/</a>"}]}